{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_51_03",
  "title": "白石沙季 3話 内緒のお祝い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　沙季ちゃんと、千紗ちゃんじゃない\n偶然ね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Isn’t that Saki and Chisa?\nWhat a coincidence~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6666668177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？\nどうしたんですか？　こんな場所に一人で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san?\nWhat are you doing here all alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ひ、一人で……あはは、そうね～……。大学の友達と\n遊ぶ予定だったんだけど、急に来れなくなっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-alone…? Ahaha‚ you’re right~. I was supposed to hang out with\na friend from college‚ but they had to cancel at the last minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9097363539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ、アイドルの、ライブのチケットがあるんだけど\nもらってくれない？　一人で行くのも、気が乗らなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That reminds me‚ I have tickets to an idol live show…\nWould you like them? I don’t really feel like going alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか？　あ、お姉ちゃん！\nこれ、お姉ちゃんが大好きなアイドルだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Ah‚ sis!\nThis is that idol group you love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "本当ね！　最近、チェック出来てなかったけど\n星見市でライブをやる予定があったなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh wow‚ you’re right!\nI didn’t know they were planning a live show in Hoshimi City!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、ダメよね\nスタンプラリーもあるし、急に行き先を変えるのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But we can’t go‚ can we?\nWe have the stamp rally‚ and changing our destination now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5666603089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫だよ、お姉ちゃん\nスタンプラリーは後でも出来るし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it’s okay‚ sis.\nWe can do the stamp rally later!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8999951681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、編集部の人達もいいって！\nせっかくの機会だから、行こう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See? The editorial staff said it’s okay!\nIt’s a rare opportunity‚ so let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.266663615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗？　なんでそんなに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa? Why are you so…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0111976148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、遠慮しないで\n私の分まで、二人で楽しんできて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ don’t be shy.\nYou two go and have fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2666613263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……そうね、せっかくだから行きましょうか\nありがとうございます、譲っていただいて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san… Okay‚ since it’s a good opportunity‚ let’s go.\nThank you for giving them to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5999946596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで\n私も、もらってくれる人がいて助かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it.\nI’m glad someone can use them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7666567487,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3160.001271400006,
          "startTime": 83.9266580201
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、自然に渡せたかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I wonder if I handed them over smoothly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5531876645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.410018182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.410018182
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.410018182
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～～～～～～～～、良かった～～～～！！\nやっぱり生で観ると格別ねっ！　もう皆可愛くって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaaaaaaaaah‚ that was amaaaaaaazing！！\nSeeing them live is something else! They were all so cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.606204184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 101.6113675675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "今回は意外な選曲もあったわよね\n忘れないうちに、セトリを書き出しておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They had some surprising songs in their setlist this time.\nI have to write down the setlist before I forget it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.133332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.2227964642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、お姉ちゃん、楽しそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you look happy‚ sis.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2227964642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.6761298022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……やだ、私ったら何してるのかしら\nお仕事の最中なのに、つい舞い上がっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Oh no‚ what am I doing?\nI’m supposed to be working‚ but I got totally carried away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9999987287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.7233102005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくて大丈夫だよ。実はね\nこれも私と編集部の人達からのプレゼントだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry about it‚ it’s fine.\nActually‚ this is also a present from me and the editorial staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3593381252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.7593446256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "スタンプラリーの四つ目の場所……\n『ひみつ』の場所は、このライブハウスのことだったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fourth location on the stamp rally…\n“Secret” was this live house!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333274844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 134.1926653704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったの？\nじゃあ、遙子さんも千紗を手伝ってくれていたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?\nSo‚ Haruko-san helped you too‚ Chisa?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0666486107,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 140.1040806612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、スタンプラリーの最後のチェックポイントだし\nびっくりすることがしたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I wanted to do something surprising\nfor the last checkpoint of the stamp rally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.366657766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 146.7475601675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、スタンプカード出して？\nこれで……んしょ。四つ揃ったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sis‚ let me see your stamp card.\nThere… Done. You’ve collected all four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.3608935268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.8789755029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、ついにゴールね\n今日一日、本当に楽しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we’ve finally reached the goal.\nI had so much fun today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9455924187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.2866635166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_03-ski011.m4a",
